05:27.400 --> 05:28.200
I looked around.

05:28.200 --> 05:29.600
There's no one else in there.

05:29.800 --> 05:31.300
Must have been a prank.

05:32.900 --> 05:34.400
Yeah, it wasn't a prank.

05:34.900 --> 05:36.000
