06:17.100 --> 06:17.700
That's him.

06:17.700 --> 06:19.600
That's the boy that I saw in the yard.

06:19.800 --> 06:22.500
That's the Bancroft's youngest son Josh.

06:22.500 --> 06:24.500
Well, It's a good bet he died at the house, then.

06:24.500 --> 06:26.700
No, I just went over all the sales paperwork,

06:26.700 --> 06:30.200
