07:34.100 --> 07:35.400
Who,  he fiancee?

07:35.400 --> 07:38.400
She is not his fiancee until he puts a ring on her finger.

07:38.400 --> 07:40.300
It's ok, honey, Just breathe.

07:40.300 --> 07:43.100
I know that he just wants to find her

07:43.100 --> 07:45.500
