12:38.600 --> 12:39.800
Hi, Mrs. Bancroft,

12:39.800 --> 12:40.800
I have a delivery for you.

12:41.000 --> 12:42.300
Well, please, come on in.

12:42.300 --> 12:43.200
Thank you.

12:43.500 --> 12:46.100
My name is Melinda Gordon. I'm friends with Delia,

12:46.100 --> 12:47.600
who's selling your grandview house,

12:47.600 --> 12:49.200
And I've been helping her stage it.

12:49.300 --> 12:51.200
Anyway, when I saw this, um,

12:53.700 --> 12:55.200
I thought that you would want it.

12:58.400 --> 13:00.000
Thank you for coming all the way out here,

13:00.000 --> 13:02.100
But, uh, no, I don't, actually...

13:02.700 --> 13:04.200
want this.

13:04.800 --> 13:05.700
Would you tell your friend

13:05.700 --> 13:07.100
that I don't want anything

13:07.100 --> 13:08.300
from that house?

13:10.500 --> 13:12.600
Ok, Well, I'm sorry for the confusion.

13:12.600 --> 13:15.100
I guess your style here is different.

13:15.100 --> 13:16.500
It's lovely.

13:17.200 --> 13:18.400
Thank you.

13:19.100 --> 13:20.800
I just needed a change.

13:22.500 --> 13:23.900
A fresh start.

13:24.100 --> 13:26.400
I've been feeling the same way recently.

13:26.900 --> 13:29.300
I just lost my husband, so...

13:29.700 --> 13:31.300
Oh, I'm sorry.

13:31.600 --> 13:34.500
So am I. About your son.

13:36.300 --> 13:37.800
How did you get through it?

13:38.400 --> 13:41.700
I just... knew he'd be with me.

13:42.100 --> 13:44.100
Wherever I went.

13:44.400 --> 13:45.700
And...

13:47.400 --> 13:48.500
He is.

13:51.500 --> 13:52.900
What about you?

13:53.200 --> 13:54.600
Do you feel like...

13:55.200 --> 13:57.100
Here that your son is with you?

13:58.200 --> 14:00.400
Well, he's in my heart always.

14:02.700 --> 14:04.600
But I didn't move

14:04.600 --> 14:06.700
