14:07.400 --> 14:09.000
My older son, he's in college,

14:09.000 --> 14:10.600
And my husband and I are...

14:11.500 --> 14:13.500
divorced, and...

14:14.100 --> 14:15.900
I did try not to blame him.

14:16.600 --> 14:19.200
